<h2><img src="/media/13048905/inghams_plus.png" alt="Inghams Plus" rel="200,33" /></h2>
<p><strong>FREE</strong> Glacier Express souvenir strap N.B. provided upon arrival in Zermatt, one per booking <br /><strong>EARLY BOOKING OFFER SAVE</strong> up to £200 per couple (ends 31 Dec)* This discount has automatically been included in the price shown.<br />* Based on 4-star holiday.</p>
<h2>What’s included</h2>
<p><strong>• Discount Travel Card - worth £100</strong><br /><strong> • Scheduled return flights from the UK to Switzerland</strong><br /><strong> • 2nd class rail transfers within Switzerland (some change of trains required, 1st class upgrade possible)</strong><br /><strong> • Services of Inghams Representatives in each resort</strong><br /><strong> • Full day excursion on the famous Glacier Express train</strong><br /><strong> • Accommodation with breakfast and dinner daily. All rooms with private facilities</strong><br /><strong> • Walking opportunities in Davos or Klosters with unlimited use of the lifts and buses</strong></p>
<p>Please note: This is an independent rail holiday and guests are free to choose their own itinerary in each resort. The above is only a suggested itinerary and excursions marked ‘optional’ are not included in the price of your holiday. An Inghams Representative is based in each resort and will provide advice and offer optional excursions and walking passes.</p>
<h2>OPTIONAL UPGRADES</h2>
<p>• <strong>Upgrade to 1st class</strong> on all four of your scenic rail transfers within Switzerland for just £72 (pre-bookable)<br />• <strong>Enjoy lunch on the Glacier Express</strong> with a simple 3 course set menu (approx. Sfr43, payable locally, please request at time of booking)<br />NB. Places are limited and cannot be guaranteed. Special diets, including vegetarian, cannot be catered for.</p>
