<p><br />Interlaken <a data-udi="umb://document/8a732f156c174b128f8f1da58ac0b10c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8a732f156c174b128f8f1da58ac0b10c}" title="Hotel Metropole">Metropole</a> ****<br />Zermatt <a data-udi="umb://document/7b472ab866b14527be25caad79fb5068" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7b472ab866b14527be25caad79fb5068}" title="Hotel Mirabeau">Mirabeau</a> ****+<br />Davos <a data-udi="umb://document/67ba36a931fc4fac83b977d22cb30b13" href="/{localLink:umb://document/67ba36a931fc4fac83b977d22cb30b13}" title="Hotel Seehof">Seehof</a> *****</p>
<p><strong>10 night holiday</strong><br />3 nights in Interlaken <br />4 nights in Zermatt<br />3 nights in Klosters or Davos<br /><strong>11 night holiday</strong><br />4 nights in Interlaken<br />3 nights in Zermatt<br />4 nights in Klosters or Davos</p>
